original_text: OWH offers easy-to-read publications on a variety of health topics. Download or order free copies in English and Spanish, and download select materials in additional languages. Sub-Topic Paragraphs FR...

qa_pairs.text_input: How can I access women's health publications offered by OWH?
qa_pairs.output: You can download or order free easy-to-read copies of women's health publications in English and Spanish from the OWH website.

qa_pairs.text_input: In what languages are OWH's women's health materials available?
qa_pairs.output: OWH's women's health materials are available in English, Spanish, and select other languages.

qa_pairs.text_input: How can I stay up-to-date on women's health news and alerts from OWH?
qa_pairs.output: You can subscribe to receive the OWH monthly newsletter and important women's health news alerts by email.
